Features

Zero Dependencies: The entire application (structure, styles, and logic) lives in one single file.
Dynamic Item Management: Add, edit, or remove invoice line items seamlessly with instant DOM updates.
Real-time Calculations: Instant automatic math updates for item subtotals, custom tax rates, discounts, and the final grand total.
Print-Ready UI: Built-in CSS print media queries that format the invoice perfectly for physical printing or direct saving as a PDF.
100% Client-Side: Runs entirely in the browser, ensuring data privacy since no invoice information ever leaves the computer.

Technology Stack
HTML5: Structured semantic forms, data tables, and user input fields.
Embedded CSS3: Clean layouts using Flexbox/Grid, paired with dedicated `@media print` rules for paper-accurate layouts.
Inline JavaScript (ES6): Real-time event listeners (`oninput`, `click`), dynamic row generation, and calculation math.

 Quick Start / Installation

Because this application is self-contained in a single file, setup is instantaneous.

1.  Clone the repository:
    ```bash
    git clone https://github.com
    ```
2.  Open the application:
    Simply double-click the `index.html` file to launch the generator immediately in any web browser. 
OR

You can simply copy the `index.html` file directly to a USB drive or your desktop and use it completely offline.*

